{"tid":1245744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明：（抗爭）只有一個方法","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:50:48.000Z","uid":389,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"113216ab13e5b0e045981c603b873cf193289d82","tid":1245744,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DaV5GYO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDaV5GYO.png&h=7b02e4f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係唔好諗有咩方法，繼續做，你做到之後，就會知用左咩方法"},{"pid":"3a3057cc3f73c0a2124216facf8611f09b64236e","tid":1245744,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"咪撚搞鳩老黎喇屌你老母"},{"pid":"0d31bcf2ab2ac05f45285865e8fe64e7ab97220f","tid":1245744,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"Up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我道行未夠 領悟唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95be2bbceef588f3fc7486925803c62a137c8538","tid":1245744,"uid":156936,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n【不內哄、不分化、各自上山】<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>======20/6/2019 17:00更新======</strong></span><br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34yGdCf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34yGdCf.jpg&h=2aced7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gB8C11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gB8C11.jpg&h=f5e08abb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n1.急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n2.立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">[全力推] 621 CONTENT PAGE 唔好再俾膠鋪上熱門！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245051</a></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港親共商店地圖</span></span></strong><br />\n消費前，睇下呢個地圖！斷親共收入！<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IKNf97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IKNf97&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8DzBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=52d777e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IKNf97</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ece50bd5a233b5e7aff8e6b7db13f9e6d7900d","tid":1245744,"uid":42970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c735ff628b4f5492afa95e6c1d2158abda21a1","tid":1245744,"uid":70781,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"做咗之後自然知自己做乜，應該咁解"},{"pid":"375542f589287f9594a0091244c13db57d5225eb","tid":1245744,"uid":15758,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0d31bcf2ab2ac05f45285865e8fe64e7ab97220f","tid":1245744,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"Up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我道行未夠 領悟唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"咪姐係做左先 唔好淨up"},{"pid":"d52d37bb9182fa4dc6b36fa6ca7883ab40815d7a","tid":1245744,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d31bcf2ab2ac05f45285865e8fe64e7ab97220f","tid":1245744,"uid":52658,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:31.000Z","msg":"Up乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪我道行未夠 領悟唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:32:41.000Z","msg":"總有人鐘意懶高深 其實佢啫係叫你亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.g